import React from "react";
import {
  BrowserRouter,
  Route,
  Switch
} from 'react-router-dom';
import Notes from './Notes'

function App() {
  return ( <
    div className = "App" >
    <
    BrowserRouter >
    <
    Switch >
    <
    Route path = "/notes" >
    <
    Notes / >
    <
    /Route>

    <
    /Switch> <
    /BrowserRouter> <
    /div>
  )
}

export default App
